Package: geomtextpath
Type: Package
Title: Use Curved Text In Ggplot2
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Allan Cameron
Maintainer: Allan Cameron <Allan.Cameron@nhs.scot>
Description: Allows text to follow curved paths in ggplot2.
    This allows for neat labelling of curves and of plots in polar co-ordinates.
